5.How does automatic renewal work?
    Cert-manager can be use for auto renewal , It continuously monitors issued certificates and renews them before they expire, so applications can continue serving HTTPS without interruption 
      When a certificate is issued, cert-manager records its validity period cert-manager periodically checks all managed Certificate resources. Instead of waiting until the expiration date, cert-manager starts the renewal process before the certificate becomes invalid. When it's time to renew, cert-manager creates a new Certificate Request, just as it did when the certificate was first issued. Domain validation is performed again
      The CA issues a renewed certificate cert-manager replaces the contents of the existing Secret. Applications use the renewed certificate


